INSERT INTO `soal` VALUES ('6858','72','11','<p>GRAFFITI AS AN ART.</p>\r\n<p>Graffiti is a painting done on the wall by using the composition of colours,lines,shapes and volumes. It contains certain words,symbols,or sentences. People usually use a spray to make graffiti. Graffiti has been done since ancient time. There are several proofs that graffiti has been done by Ancient Roman people. However, some people still think that graffiti is a form of vandalism. We must change that paradigm. We must think graffiti as an art. There are famous artists that start their career from doing graffiti. They express their emotion and expression freely through graffiti. We can take many examples of famous artists that start their carier from doing graffiti, like Borris, Utha and Ether,Egs,Katsu and many more. Besides that,graffiti can be sign of the emergence of new language.If we look from the aspect of social psychology, people use graffiti as as a secret language that voice their disappointment towards a certain social situation. They also use graffiti as a secret language to voice their protest towards certain political and social phenomena. In other words, we must not treat graffiti as a vandalism. On the contrary,we must treat graffiti as an art and voice of reason in this chaotic world.</p>\r\n<p>What is the writer talking about ?</p>','1','<p>Graffiti as an art</p>','<p>Graffiti as a vandalism</p>','<p>Graffiti as a language</p>','<p>Graffiti as a law</p>','<p>Graffiti as the obedience to law.</p>','A','','','','','','','');
